### ========================================
### AUTHENTICATION APIs
### ========================================

### 1. Đăng nhập
POST https://localhost:7217/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Đăng ký user mới
POST https://localhost:7217/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "fullName": "New User"
}

### 3. Test JWT token (thay YOUR_TOKEN bằng token từ login)
POST https://localhost:7217/api/auth/test-token
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### ========================================
### USER PROFILE APIs
### ========================================

### 4. Lấy thông tin profile user
GET https://localhost:7217/api/user
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### 5. Cập nhật profile user
PUT https://localhost:7217/api/user/update
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Updated Name",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

### 6. Lấy danh sách CV của user
GET https://localhost:7217/api/user/cvs
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### ========================================
### CV MANAGEMENT APIs
### ========================================

### 7. Lấy danh sách CV
GET https://localhost:7217/api/cv
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### 8. Tạo CV mới (đơn giản)
POST https://localhost:7217/api/cv
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First CV",
  "isPublic": true,
  "isDefault": true
}

